[src:testify-go/assertion-software-development] The Boolean expression must be a compile-time constant value, for example `(sizeof(int)==4)` would be a valid expression in that context.
[src:testify-go/assertion-software-development] This construct does not work at file scope (i.e., not inside a function), and so it must be wrapped inside a function.
